casebody.data:
HABEAS CORPUS RESOURCE CENTER, et al., applicants,
v.
UNITED STATES DEPARTMENT OF JUSTICE, et al. No. 16A683 (16-880). Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 27, 2017.

Application to recall and stay the mandate pending disposition of the petition for writ of certiorari presented to Justice KENNEDY and by him referred to the Court denied.
